#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=WN : So none of those hurt ?
#Text=RB
#Text=:
#Text=None of these hurt .
#Text=WN : Do any of them hurt , on your face or your leg ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: None of the ones on my face hurt .
#Text=They 're just like extra growths , you know , fatty tissue .
#Text=Above my left eye there 's a lot of itching on the inside , it tingles on the inside above my eye .
#Text=WN : Where have you had surgeries ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: I had surgery on my nose , on my lip and on my cheek , and eye .
#Text=WN : Can you turn your head to the right ?
#Text=Your left ear seems to be lower .
#Text=How come ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: Right , it 's the fatty tissue and everything , it just hangs , it pulls everything down .
#Text=I have a small tumor on the optic nerve of my left eye , and it 's growing , and it 's pushing the eye outwards , and it 's out of the eye socket , and that 's what makes the eye look lower .
#Text=WN : Do you have any vision in the left eye ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: I have very little vision in the left eye .
#Text=WN : Can you make out movement ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: Well , the only way I can really see out of it is when I cover the right eye .
#Text=Then I can see out of it , I ca n't see really well , but I can count fingers from maybe about 3 feet .
#Text=WN : Tell me about your leg .
#Text=RB
#Text=: My leg is ... from the knee down , they are tumors and a lot of fatty tissue , and it swells .
#Text=It 's difficult to walk .
#Text=I have to wear a special sock to hold it together to keep it from expanding .
#Text=It 's a compression sock and it 's helped with circulation .
#Text=WN :
#Text=It looks very painful , your leg looks like it 's an S.
#Text=RB
#Text=: That 's because on the left side right here it 's just a lot of fatty tissue .
#Text=The bone is not curved it 's just , this right here is just a lot of extra tissue .
#Text=If I take the sock off it wo n't look like an S. All the fatty tissue would just drop .
#Text=So , that 's how that works .
#Text=WN : Okay , tell me about your shoe .
#Text=RB : The shoes are specially made , they 're custom made .
#Text=A cast is made and they make the shoes from the mold .
#Text=Because of the leg , I have to have special support .
#Text=WN : Can you show me the side of your foot ... and the other side ?
#Text=RB
#Text=: The shoes they help support the ankle from bending to one side .
#Text=The right foot is not affected at all , only the left side .
#Text=WN :
#Text=It looks like mainly the left side of your body is affected by NF .
